name: Ane Jaune
overview: A French language puzzle game created by Claude Baisnee and published in Hebdogiciel N°083 (17.05.1985) and N°084 (24.05.1985). You have to get the yellow square out of the box by sliding the coins to clear the way. To do this, you will place the black dot on a piece with the joystick then by pressing the red button you orient the handle in the direction where you want to move the piece. If the movement is possible, it will take place, otherwise nothing will happen. Up to you!
